item.title: What To Do When You Worry Your Great Work Is Behind You with Julie Ellis | UYGW057
item.description:
Julie Ellis, a co-founder of Mabel's labels and the author of Big Gorgeous Goals, has a unique perspective on success. When she and her co-founders sold Mabelâ€™s Labels to Avery, she felt both proud of the accomplishment and sad about losing what they had enjoyed building. This is a very common but rarely discussed part of Great Work. 

So much of what we talk about focuses on getting started and overcoming hurdles, staying at it, and building toward success... Feed: https://feeds.captivate.fm/unleashing-your-great-work/
